games.name: GalgaMulti
games.description: Controlling a starship, both players will destroy the Galga forces, while avoiding enemies. Each player has 3 lives, game ends once a player runs out of lives.

games.name: Secure the river!
games.description: This is a cooperative game where both players share lives. You must defeat skeletons, collect hearts and avoid the ducks and fishes.

games.name: Strawberry Slam
games.description: Two strawberries battle it out in the kitchen to be the Shortcake Star!

games.name: TicTacTwo!
games.description: Ultimate battle between cats and dogs! The player who succeeds in placing three of their marks in a horizontal, vertical, or diagonal row is the winner as the best pet.

games.name: Blocky Boss Battle
games.description: A test of reflexes! Avoid the blue stingers while sending fireballs at the boss!

games.name: Asphodel follows directions
games.description: Place arrows along the path to help Asphodel the witch find their way

games.name: Pigeon: Deliverance
games.description: Fly through the dangerous rooftops and ledges of New York City delivering messages!

games.name: Save the Forest
games.description: Fly your plane over the forest spraying water to put out the fires!

games.name: Falling Duck
games.description: Fly through the sky avoiding obstacles

games.name: Space Destroyer
games.description: Use the lasers on your spaceship to shoot falling asteroids!

games.name: Hot Air Balloon
games.description: Navigate your hot air balloon through the mountains avoiding birds and spaceships

games.name: Bunny Hop!
games.description: Help your bunny hop over obstacles as they run through the forest

games.name: Caterpillar
games.description: Eat the leaves to grow, but watch out for walls!

games.name: Jewel Raider
games.description: Adventure through levels collecting jewels and avoiding obstacles!

games.name: Mouse Adventure
games.description: Go on a mouse adventure in a haunted castle, battling bad guys, avoiding obstacles and collecting keys!

games.name: Cave Explorer
games.description: Explore multiple levels of caves deep within the earth, but watch out for those cave caterpillars!

games.name: Kickoff!
games.description: Time to practice your football throwing game! Coordinate plays and avoid defenders
